      "message": "Thanks for the review.\nThis was inspired by change [86156], which proposes adding PLDMSensors and Inventory to the MCTP target schema. CreateSensors controls the same PLDM sensor behavior, so it seemed like a natural fit alongside those properties.\n\nIf we separate PLDM config into its own schema, we\u0027d need a binding mechanism back to the MCTP target, which could introduce timing/race issues like those discussed in change [86228].\n\nHappy to adapt if the community prefers a different approach.\n\n[86156]: https://gerrit.openbmc.org/c/openbmc/entity-manager/+/86156\n[86228]: https://gerrit.openbmc.org/c/openbmc/pldm/+/86228",
